 in Ptolemaic Egypt (1986), S. 102</bibl><bibl type="translations" default="NO">Rowlandson, Women and Society (1998), 87</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.284" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>unbekannt</p></div></body></text></TEI.2>